{"tid":806532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"廣告竟抄襲《新海誠》動畫，南韓左翼政黨致歉","createTime":"2018-09-04T17:40:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-05T03:02:12.000Z","uid":123264,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2bd243a2d48c655177bd0cec4ed02e7dc35bf85f","tid":806532,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:40:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1592588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.gamme.com.tw%2F1592588&d=CAH5XDc4Z%2BkGYAjZ8FYluDOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=e1521d62\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.gamme.com.tw/1592588</a><br />\n<br />\n面對排山倒海而來的網路譴責聲浪，「正義黨」於8月30日發表聲明，承認影片內容盜用新海誠的《十字路口》（クロスロード）構圖分鏡，並為此正式致歉。「正義黨」表示，會出現這樣的錯誤，是因為負責製作宣傳動畫的員工本身是新海誠的狂熱粉，在工期緊迫的壓力下竟做出剽竊行為。正義黨為把關不嚴向韓國民眾及所有新海誠的粉絲致上歉意，並為侵害新海誠的權益深感愧疚，未來將更加努力保護創作者的權利。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images.gamme.com.tw/news2/2018/25/88/q5iUo52bj6Obr6U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2018%2F25%2F88%2Fq5iUo52bj6Obr6U.jpg&h=e4aa5f15&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港終於同韓狗睇齊<br />\n錯就錯在抄得太足<br />\n好似香港鳩鐵咁抄D唔抄D 仲要抄到樣樣衰衰核核突突咪唔駛比人屌囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d27ce7a25b848f129e331af4b6a17e81a9b1eb3c","tid":806532,"uid":29014,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"樓主我勸你走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c8626cb75e77520eda2ec258290364f1e245d47","tid":806532,"uid":117200,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T18:02:05.000Z","msg":"屌佢呢d仲衰過抄喎,直頭係照copy"},{"pid":"47cc95db4a21adc0284285092641e068b37f6eb8","tid":806532,"uid":61954,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"d27ce7a25b848f129e331af4b6a17e81a9b1eb3c","tid":806532,"uid":29014,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T17:45:56.000Z","msg":"樓主我勸你走先<img src=\